[Automatic Restart] (Ref: https://blog.hyunsub.kim/Spring/Spring-with-Terminal/)
$ ./gradlew build -continuous   # Terminal 1
$ ./gradlew bootRun             # Terminal 2


[Regularly Creating Log File]
- logback-spring.xml의 fileNamePattern 조작
- yearly: %d{yyyy}-%i.log
- monthly: %d{yyyy-MM}-%i.log
- daily: %d{yyyy-MM-dd}-%i.log
- hourly: %d{yyyy-MM-dd-HH}-%i.log
- minutely: %d{yyyy-MM-dd-HH-mm}-%i.log
- secondly: %d{yyyy-MM-dd-HH-mm-ss}-%i.log


[설정파일(yml, properties)에서 classpath 의미]
- classpath: resources를 rootPath로 지정한다는 뜻


